&lt;h1 id="some-heroes"&gt;Some Heroes&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;April 2008&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There are some topics I save up because they&amp;rsquo;ll be so much fun to write about. This is one of them: a list of my heroes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m not claiming this is a list of the n most admirable people. Who could make such a list, even if they wanted to? Einstein isn&amp;rsquo;t on the list, for example, even though he probably deserves to be on any shortlist of admirable people. I once asked a physicist friend if Einstein was really as smart as his fame implies, and she said that yes, he was. So why isn&amp;rsquo;t he on the list? Because I had to ask. This is a list of people who&amp;rsquo;ve influenced me, not people who would have if I understood their work.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>